      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      mysql-server \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 -y && \
      echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh" >> ~/.bashrc && \
      echo "conda activate flex-env" >> ~/.bashrc
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda activate flex-env && \
      conda install -c conda-forge r-base r-eva -y && \
      conda install -y pip pytest pytest-timeout && \
      pip install arviz==0.6.1 rpy2==3.2.0 scipy==1.5.4 && \
      pip install jax==0.2.9 jaxlib==0.1.61 && \
      pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN echo "jax==0.2.9" > tool/scripts/extra_deps/coax.txt
  RUN cat > tool/scripts/get_setup_extras.py << 'EOF'
  #!/usr/bin/env python
  import ast
  import astunparse
  import sys
  import os
  def extract_extras_require(setup_file):
      try:
          with open(setup_file, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:
              content = f.read()
      except UnicodeDecodeError:
          with open(setup_file, 'r', encoding='latin-1') as f:
              content = f.read()
      tree = ast.parse(content)
      for node in ast.walk(tree):
          if isinstance(node, ast.Call):
              if hasattr(node.func, 'id') and node.func.id == 'setup':
                  for keyword in node.keywords:
                      if keyword.arg == 'extras_require':
                          extras_dict = {}
                          if isinstance(keyword.value, ast.Dict):
                              for key, value in zip(keyword.value.keys, keyword.value.values):
                                  if isinstance(key, ast.Str):
                                      key_str = key.s
                                  elif isinstance(key, ast.Constant):
                                      key_str = key.value
                                  else:
                                      continue
                                  deps = []
                                  if isinstance(value, ast.List):
                                      for dep in value.elts:
                                          if isinstance(dep, ast.Str):
                                              deps.append(dep.s)
                                          elif isinstance(dep, ast.Constant):
                                              deps.append(dep.value)
                                  extras_dict[key_str] = deps
                          # Generate printExtra.py
                          print_extra_content = "#!/usr/bin/env python\n"
                          print_extra_content += "extras = " + repr(extras_dict) + "\n"
                          print_extra_content += "for key, deps in extras.items():\n"
                          print_extra_content += "    for dep in deps:\n"
                          print_extra_content += "        print(f'dep>{dep}')\n"
                          output_file = os.path.join(os.path.dirname(setup_file), 'printExtra.py')
                          with open(output_file, 'w') as f:
                              f.write(print_extra_content)
                          return extras_dict
      return {}
  if __name__ == "__main__":
      if len(sys.argv) > 1:
          setup_file = sys.argv[1]
          extras = extract_extras_require(setup_file)
          print("Extracted extras_require:", extras)
      else:
          print("Usage: python get_setup_extras.py <setup.py>")
  EOF
  RUN chmod +x tool/scripts/get_setup_extras.py
  RUN source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda activate flex-env && \
      pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda activate flex-env && \
      conda env export > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  CMD ["/bin/bash"]
--- End of Iteration 1 ---

  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ENV TZ=UTC
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      wget \
      git \
      curl \
      build-essential \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev \
      libsdl-mixer1.2-dev \
      libsdl-ttf2.0-dev \
      libsdl1.2-dev \
      libsmpeg-dev \
      subversion \
      libportmidi-dev \
      ffmpeg \
      libswscale-dev \
      libavformat-dev \
      libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev \
      libasound2-dev \
      libjack-dev \
      portaudio19-dev \
      libsndfile1-dev \
      pkg-config \
      libgmp3-dev \
      libopenmpi-dev \
      libeigen3-dev \
      cmake \
      libgl1-mesa-dev \
      libsdl2-dev \
      libsdl2-image-dev \
      libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev \
      libboost-all-dev \
      libdirectfb-dev \
      libst-dev \
      mesa-utils \
      xvfb \
      x11vnc \
      libsdl-sge-dev \
      libmysqlclient-dev \
      libmariadbclient-dev \
      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      mysql-server \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 -y && \
      echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh" >> ~/.bashrc && \
      echo "conda activate flex-env" >> ~/.bashrc
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda activate flex-env && \
      conda install -c conda-forge r-base r-eva -y && \
      conda install -y pip pytest pytest-timeout && \
      pip install arviz==0.6.1 rpy2==3.2.0 scipy==1.5.4 && \
      pip install jax==0.2.9 jaxlib==0.1.61 && \
      pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda activate flex-env && \
      pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda activate flex-env && \
      conda env export > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  CMD ["/bin/bash"]

  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ENV TZ=UTC
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      wget \
      git \
      curl \
      build-essential \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev \
      libsdl-mixer1.2-dev \
      libsdl-ttf2.0-dev \
      libsdl1.2-dev \
      libsmpeg-dev \
      subversion \
      libportmidi-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      ffmpeg \
      libswscale-dev \
      libavformat-dev \
      libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev \
      libasound2-dev \
      libjack-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      portaudio19-dev \
      libsndfile1-dev \
      pkg-config \
      libgmp3-dev \
      libopenmpi-dev \
      libeigen3-dev \
      cmake \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libgl1-mesa-dev \
      libsdl2-dev \
      libsdl2-image-dev \
      libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev \
      libboost-all-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libdirectfb-dev \
      libst-dev \
      mesa-utils \
      xvfb \
      x11vnc \
      libsdl-sge-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libmysqlclient-dev \
      libmariadbclient-dev \
      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      mysql-server \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 -y && \
      echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh" >> ~/.bashrc && \
      echo "conda activate flex-env" >> ~/.bashrc
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda activate flex-env && \
      conda install -c conda-forge r-base r-eva -y && \
      conda install -y pip pytest pytest-timeout && \
      pip install arviz==0.6.1 rpy2==3.2.0 scipy==1.5.4 && \
      pip install jax==0.2.9 jaxlib==0.1.61 && \
      pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda activate flex-env && \
      pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda activate flex-env && \
      conda env export > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  CMD ["/bin/bash"]

  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ENV TZ=UTC
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      wget \
      git \
      curl \
      build-essential \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev \
      libsdl-mixer1.2-dev \
      libsdl-ttf2.0-dev \
      libsdl1.2-dev \
      libsmpeg-dev \
      subversion \
      libportmidi-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      ffmpeg \
      libswscale-dev \
      libavformat-dev \
      libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev \
      libasound2-dev \
      libjack-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      portaudio19-dev \
      libsndfile1-dev \
      pkg-config \
      libgmp3-dev \
      libopenmpi-dev \
      libeigen3-dev \
      cmake \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libgl1-mesa-dev \
      libsdl2-dev \
      libsdl2-image-dev \
      libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev \
      libboost-all-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libdirectfb-dev \
      libst-dev \
      mesa-utils \
      xvfb \
      x11vnc \
      libsdl-sge-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libmysqlclient-dev \
      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 -y && \
      echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh" >> ~/.bashrc && \
      echo "conda activate flex-env" >> ~/.bashrc
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda activate flex-env && \
      conda install -c conda-forge r-base r-eva -y && \
      conda install -y pip pytest pytest-timeout && \
      pip install arviz==0.6.1 rpy2==3.2.0 scipy==1.5.4 && \
      pip install jax==0.2.9 jaxlib==0.1.61 && \
      pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda activate flex-env && \
      pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda activate flex-env && \
      conda env export > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  CMD ["/bin/bash"]

      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \

NEXT:
  current progress
  The Dockerfile has successfully installed all system dependencies and created the basic directory structure. However, the conda environment creation failed during the build process. The error occurred at the conda init and conda create commands, likely due to the conda installation not being properly initialized in the Docker build context.
  next step
  Replace the failing conda commands with a proper initialization sequence. Change lines 83-84 from:
  ```
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda init bash && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 -y --solver=classic
  ```
  to:
  ```
  RUN echo ". /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh" >> ~/.bashrc && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 -y
  ```
  This avoids the conda init command which requires a shell restart and removes the --solver=classic flag which may not be available in all conda versions.

      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

      libsdl-image1.2-dev \

      portaudio19-dev \
      libsndfile1-dev \
      pkg-config \
      libgmp3-dev \
      libopenmpi-dev \
      libeigen3-dev \
      cmake \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libgl1-mesa-dev \
      libsdl2-dev \
      libsdl2-image-dev \
      libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev \
      libboost-all-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libdirectfb-dev \
      libst-dev \
      mesa-utils \
      xvfb \
      x11vnc \
      libsdl-sge-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libmysqlclient-dev \
      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda init bash && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 -y --solver=classic
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -c conda-forge r-base r-eva -y && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -y pip pytest pytest-timeout && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install arviz==0.6.1 rpy2==3.2.0 scipy==1.5.4 && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install jax==0.2.9 jaxlib==0.1.61 && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda env export -n flex-env > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  RUN echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda activate flex-env" >> /home/cc/.bashrc
  CMD ["/bin/bash", "-l"]

  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ENV TZ=UTC
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      wget \
      git \
      curl \
      build-essential \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev \
      libsdl-mixer1.2-dev \
      libsdl-ttf2.0-dev \
      libsdl1.2-dev \
      libsmpeg-dev \
      subversion \
      libportmidi-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

      ffmpeg \
      libswscale-dev \
      libavformat-dev \
      libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev \
      libasound2-dev \
      libjack-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      portaudio19-dev \
      libsndfile1-dev \
      pkg-config \
      libgmp3-dev \
      libopenmpi-dev \
      libeigen3-dev \
      cmake \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libgl1-mesa-dev \
      libsdl2-dev \
      libsdl2-image-dev \
      libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev \
      libboost-all-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libdirectfb-dev \
      libst-dev \
      mesa-utils \
      xvfb \
      x11vnc \
      libsdl-sge-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libmysqlclient-dev \
      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN echo ". /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh" >> ~/.bashrc && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 -y
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -c conda-forge r-base r-eva -y && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -y pip pytest pytest-timeout && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install arviz==0.6.1 rpy2==3.2.0 scipy==1.5.4 && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install jax==0.2.9 jaxlib==0.1.61 && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda env export -n flex-env > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  RUN echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda activate flex-env" >> /home/cc/.bashrc
  CMD ["/bin/bash", "-l"]

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ENV TZ=UTC
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      wget \
      git \
      curl \
      build-essential \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev \
      libsdl-mixer1.2-dev \
      libsdl-ttf2.0-dev \
      libsdl1.2-dev \
      libsmpeg-dev \
      subversion \
      libportmidi-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      ffmpeg \
      libswscale-dev \
      libavformat-dev \
      libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev \
      libasound2-dev \
      libjack-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      portaudio19-dev \
      libsndfile1-dev \
      pkg-config \
      libgmp3-dev \
      libopenmpi-dev \
      libeigen3-dev \
      cmake \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libgl1-mesa-dev \
      libsdl2-dev \
      libsdl2-image-dev \
      libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev \
      libboost-all-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libdirectfb-dev \
      libst-dev \
      mesa-utils \
      xvfb \
      x11vnc \
      libsdl-sge-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libmysqlclient-dev \
      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda init bash && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 -y
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -c conda-forge r-base r-eva -y && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -y pip pytest pytest-timeout && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install arviz==0.6.1 rpy2==3.2.0 scipy==1.5.4 && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install jax==0.2.9 jaxlib==0.1.61 && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda env export -n flex-env > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  RUN echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda activate flex-env" >> /home/cc/.bashrc
  CMD ["/bin/bash", "-l"]

  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ENV TZ=UTC
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      wget \
      git \
      curl \
      build-essential \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev \
      libsdl-mixer1.2-dev \
      libsdl-ttf2.0-dev \
      libsdl1.2-dev \
      libsmpeg-dev \
      subversion \
      libportmidi-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      ffmpeg \
      libswscale-dev \
      libavformat-dev \
      libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev \
      libasound2-dev \
      libjack-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      portaudio19-dev \
      libsndfile1-dev \
      pkg-config \
      libgmp3-dev \
      libopenmpi-dev \
      libeigen3-dev \
      cmake \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libgl1-mesa-dev \
      libsdl2-dev \
      libsdl2-image-dev \
      libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev \
      libboost-all-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libdirectfb-dev \
      libst-dev \
      mesa-utils \
      xvfb \
      x11vnc \
      libsdl-sge-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libmysqlclient-dev \
      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda init bash
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN source /home/cc/.bashrc && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda update -n base -c defaults conda -y && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda config --add channels conda-forge && \
      /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 -y
  RUN source /home/cc/.bashrc && \
      source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda activate flex-env && \
      conda install -c conda-forge r-base r-eva -y && \
      conda install -y pip pytest pytest-timeout && \
      pip install arviz==0.6.1 rpy2==3.2.0 scipy==1.5.4 && \
      pip install jax==0.2.9 jaxlib==0.1.61 && \
      pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN source /home/cc/.bashrc && \
      source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda activate flex-env && \
      pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda env export -n flex-env > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  RUN echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda activate flex-env" >> /home/cc/.bashrc
  CMD ["/bin/bash", "-l"]

  ENV TZ=UTC
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      wget \
      git \
      curl \
      build-essential \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev \
      libsdl-mixer1.2-dev \
      libsdl-ttf2.0-dev \
      libsdl1.2-dev \
      libsmpeg-dev \

      ffmpeg \
      libswscale-dev \

      libfreetype6-dev \
      libasound2-dev \
      libjack-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

      portaudio19-dev \
      libsndfile1-dev \
      pkg-config \
      libgmp3-dev \
      libopenmpi-dev \

      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

      libsdl2-ttf-dev \

      libdirectfb-dev \
      libst-dev \
      mesa-utils \

      libmysqlclient-dev \
      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda init bash
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]

  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda env export -n flex-env > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ENV TZ=UTC
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      wget \
      git \
      curl \
      build-essential \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev \
      libsdl-mixer1.2-dev \
      libsdl-ttf2.0-dev \
      libsdl1.2-dev \
      libsmpeg-dev \
      subversion \
      libportmidi-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      ffmpeg \
      libswscale-dev \
      libavformat-dev \
      libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev \
      libasound2-dev \
      libjack-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      portaudio19-dev \
      libsndfile1-dev \
      pkg-config \
      libgmp3-dev \
      libopenmpi-dev \
      libeigen3-dev \
      cmake \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libgl1-mesa-dev \
      libsdl2-dev \
      libsdl2-image-dev \
      libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev \
      libboost-all-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libdirectfb-dev \
      libst-dev \
      mesa-utils \
      xvfb \
      x11vnc \
      libsdl-sge-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libmysqlclient-dev \
      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda init bash
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda config --add channels conda-forge
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 -y
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -c conda-forge r-base r-eva -y
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -y pip pytest pytest-timeout
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install arviz==0.6.1 rpy2==3.2.0 scipy==1.5.4
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install jax==0.2.9 jaxlib==0.1.61
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda env export -n flex-env > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  RUN echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda activate flex-env" >> /home/cc/.bashrc
  CMD ["/bin/bash", "-l"]

  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ENV TZ=UTC
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      wget \
      git \
      curl \
      build-essential \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev \
      libsdl-mixer1.2-dev \
      libsdl-ttf2.0-dev \
      libsdl1.2-dev \
      libsmpeg-dev \
      subversion \
      libportmidi-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

      ffmpeg \
      libswscale-dev \
      libavformat-dev \
      libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev \
      libasound2-dev \
      libjack-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

      portaudio19-dev \
      libsndfile1-dev \
      pkg-config \
      libgmp3-dev \
      libopenmpi-dev \
      libeigen3-dev \
      cmake \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libgl1-mesa-dev \
      libsdl2-dev \
      libsdl2-image-dev \
      libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev \
      libboost-all-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libdirectfb-dev \
      libst-dev \
      mesa-utils \
      xvfb \
      x11vnc \
      libsdl-sge-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libmysqlclient-dev \
      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda init bash
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda config --add channels conda-forge
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda create -n flex-env -c defaults -c conda-forge python=3.8 -y --debug
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -c conda-forge r-base r-eva -y
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -y pip pytest pytest-timeout
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install arviz==0.6.1 rpy2==3.2.0 scipy==1.5.4
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install jax==0.2.9 jaxlib==0.1.61
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda env export -n flex-env > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  RUN echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda activate flex-env" >> /home/cc/.bashrc
  CMD ["/bin/bash", "-l"]

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ENV TZ=UTC
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      wget \
      git \
      curl \
      build-essential \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev \
      libsdl-mixer1.2-dev \
      libsdl-ttf2.0-dev \
      libsdl1.2-dev \
      libsmpeg-dev \
      subversion \
      libportmidi-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      ffmpeg \
      libswscale-dev \
      libavformat-dev \
      libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev \
      libasound2-dev \
      libjack-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      portaudio19-dev \
      libsndfile1-dev \
      pkg-config \
      libgmp3-dev \
      libopenmpi-dev \
      libeigen3-dev \
      cmake \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libgl1-mesa-dev \
      libsdl2-dev \
      libsdl2-image-dev \
      libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev \
      libboost-all-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libdirectfb-dev \
      libst-dev \
      mesa-utils \
      xvfb \
      x11vnc \
      libsdl-sge-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libmysqlclient-dev \
      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda init bash
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda config --add channels conda-forge
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 -y
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -c conda-forge r-base r-eva -y
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -y pip pytest pytest-timeout
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install arviz==0.6.1 rpy2==3.2.0 scipy==1.5.4
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install jax==0.2.9 jaxlib==0.1.61
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda env export -n flex-env > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  RUN echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda activate flex-env" >> /home/cc/.bashrc
  CMD ["/bin/bash", "-l"]

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ENV TZ=UTC
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      wget \
      git \
      curl \
      build-essential \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev \
      libsdl-mixer1.2-dev \
      libsdl-ttf2.0-dev \
      libsdl1.2-dev \
      libsmpeg-dev \
      subversion \
      libportmidi-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      ffmpeg \
      libswscale-dev \
      libavformat-dev \
      libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev \
      libasound2-dev \
      libjack-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      portaudio19-dev \
      libsndfile1-dev \
      pkg-config \
      libgmp3-dev \
      libopenmpi-dev \
      libeigen3-dev \
      cmake \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libgl1-mesa-dev \
      libsdl2-dev \
      libsdl2-image-dev \
      libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev \
      libboost-all-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libdirectfb-dev \
      libst-dev \
      mesa-utils \
      xvfb \
      x11vnc \
      libsdl-sge-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libmysqlclient-dev \
      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda init bash
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda config --add channels conda-forge
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda update -n base conda -y
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda create -n flex-env --solver=classic -y
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda install -n flex-env python=3.8 -y
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -c conda-forge r-base r-eva -y
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -y pip pytest pytest-timeout
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install arviz==0.6.1 rpy2==3.2.0 scipy==1.5.4
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install jax==0.2.9 jaxlib==0.1.61
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda env export -n flex-env > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  RUN echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda activate flex-env" >> /home/cc/.bashrc
  CMD ["/bin/bash", "-l"]

      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      portaudio19-dev \
      libsndfile1-dev \
      pkg-config \
      libgmp3-dev \
      libopenmpi-dev \
      libeigen3-dev \
      cmake \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libgl1-mesa-dev \
      libsdl2-dev \
      libsdl2-image-dev \
      libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev \
      libboost-all-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libdirectfb-dev \
      libst-dev \
      mesa-utils \
      xvfb \
      x11vnc \
      libsdl-sge-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libmysqlclient-dev \
      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda init bash
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda config --add channels conda-forge
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 --solver=classic -y
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -c conda-forge r-base r-eva -y
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -y pip pytest pytest-timeout
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install arviz==0.6.1 rpy2==3.2.0 scipy==1.5.4
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install jax==0.2.9 jaxlib==0.1.61
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda env export -n flex-env > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  RUN echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda activate flex-env" >> /home/cc/.bashrc
  CMD ["/bin/bash", "-l"]

  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda env export -n flex-env > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  RUN echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda activate flex-env" >> /home/cc/.bashrc
  CMD ["/bin/bash", "-l"]

      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen

  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \

  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 --solver=classic -y

  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}

  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda env export -n flex-env > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  RUN echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda activate flex-env" >> /home/cc/.bashrc
  CMD ["/bin/bash", "-l"]

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  ENV TZ=UTC
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      wget \
      git \
      curl \
      build-essential \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev \
      libsdl-mixer1.2-dev \
      libsdl-ttf2.0-dev \
      libsdl1.2-dev \
      libsmpeg-dev \
      subversion \
      libportmidi-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      ffmpeg \
      libswscale-dev \
      libavformat-dev \
      libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev \
      libasound2-dev \
      libjack-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      portaudio19-dev \
      libsndfile1-dev \
      pkg-config \
      libgmp3-dev \
      libopenmpi-dev \
      libeigen3-dev \
      cmake \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libgl1-mesa-dev \
      libsdl2-dev \
      libsdl2-image-dev \
      libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev \
      libboost-all-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libdirectfb-dev \
      libst-dev \
      mesa-utils \
      xvfb \
      x11vnc \
      libsdl-sge-dev \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \
      libmysqlclient-dev \
      libpq-dev \
      gdal-bin \
      libgdal-dev \
      clang \
      swig \
      && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  RUN ln -sf /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h && \
      ln -sf /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen
  RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash cc
  USER cc
  WORKDIR /home/cc
  RUN wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /home/cc/miniconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/home/cc/miniconda3/bin:${PATH}"
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda init bash
  SHELL ["/bin/bash", "-c"]
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda config --add channels conda-forge
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda create -n flex-env python=3.8 -y
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -c conda-forge r-base r-eva -y
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env conda install -y pip pytest pytest-timeout
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install arviz==0.6.1 rpy2==3.2.0 scipy==1.5.4
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install jax==0.2.9 jaxlib==0.1.61
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip install astunparse numpy statsmodels hyperopt tabulate pandas diff-match-patch
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/{projects,tool/logs,tool/scripts/extra_deps,test_results,patches,diffs,build_logs,tool/scripts/data,tool/scripts/azure/results,obj}
  WORKDIR /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex
  COPY --chown=cc:cc . .
  RUN echo -e '.idea/\n*.pyc\n__pycache__\nvenv\nlogs/\ntool/scripts/data\n.vscode\nobj/\nprojects/\n*.tar.gz\nbuild_logs/\ntool/scripts/azure/results/' > .gitignore
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda run -n flex-env pip freeze > requirements-frozen.txt
  RUN /home/cc/miniconda3/bin/conda env export -n flex-env > environment.yml
  RUN echo "flex-env created on $(date)" > conda_environments.txt
  RUN echo "source /home/cc/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda activate flex-env" >> /home/cc/.bashrc
  CMD ["/bin/bash", "-l"]
